  m_Name: SM Morning 2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Dialog
  lines:
  - speaker: You
    line: "Well word around the street is that there\u2019s been a series of incidents
      happening around here. "
    SpriteRange: 5
  - speaker: You
    line: So best be careful.
    SpriteRange: 5
  - speaker: ???
    line: "Oh that\u2019s no worry to me. "
    SpriteRange: 5
  - speaker: ???
    line: "I\u2019m rather capable of defending myself. "
    SpriteRange: 4
  - speaker: ???
    line: "However, I must ask why you\u2019re here by yourself at this time."
    SpriteRange: 5
  - speaker: You
    line: "I\u2019m uhhh... heading to work. I just like to take a longer route to
      pass the time."
    SpriteRange: 5
  - speaker: ???
    line: My work at this hour? You sure are committed.
    SpriteRange: 6
  - speaker: You
    line: Thanks..
    SpriteRange: 6
